[I] A QtQuick plugin providing high-performance charts

[T] The Quick Charts module provides a set of charts that can be used from
[T] QtQuick applications. They are intended to be used for both simple display
[T] of data as well as continuous display of high-volume data

[U] https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/kquickcharts

